sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Copilot
    participant A as analyze
    participant H as highlight
    participant D as drilldown
    participant E as export

    U->>C: codewalker プロンプト選択
    C->>A: analyze(filePath, symbolName)
    A-->>C: sourceCode + blocks + cache?

    C->>H: highlight(blocks, annotations, explanations)
    H-->>C: OK
    Note over C: チャットで概要説明

    loop 質問ループ
        C->>D: drilldown()
        D-->>C: question / finished
        alt finished
            C->>E: export(filePath, symbolName, blocks)
            E-->>C: saved paths
        else question
            Note over C: チャットで回答
        end
    end
